dct_title_s: A map of Virginia and Maryland
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. From: Speed, John. A prospect of the most famous parts of the world. London. 1676. Engraved by: F. Lamb. Derived from Augustine Herrman map of 1673. Text on verso: The description of Mary-land. The description of Virginia.
dct_publisher_sm: [London] : Sold by Thomas Basset in Fleetstreet and Richard Chiswell in St. Pauls Church yard, [1676]
